narratives.question_text:
Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
(Your anonymous response to this question may be viewed by Yale College students, faculty, and advisers to aid in course selection and evaluating teaching.)
comments: I would recommend this course to another student. It is overall a really great course with a lot to gain from it. The assignments were extremely prevalent to current-day issues, and it was nice to think through them critically, especially as programmers.

I would recommend this course to another student. I found the seminar discussion format to be very refreshing and the opportunity to learn and grow among a small group of peers, some with professional experience about the topics we discussed, to be very valuable.
